---
title: Crispy Chicken in Sweet Teriyaki Sauce with rice and pan-fried broccolini
description: The tangy umami flavour of teriyaki meets sweet chilli sauce in this Asian-fusion recipe. Fragrant rice, crisp broccolini and crispier crumbed chicken are the perfect vehicle for the sticky and addictive sauce that dominates this dinnertime dish.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y24_R05_W32_IE_IECFC21558-2_MAIN_high-e00b4040.jpg
